stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Pending
    Pending --> Approved: "Moderator approves"
    Pending --> Rejected: "Moderator rejects"
    Pending --> Hidden: "Hidden due to moderation policy"
    Approved --> Hidden: "Later hidden after report/decision"
    Hidden --> Approved: "Restore if admin decides"
    Rejected --> [*]
    Approved --> [*]

    note right of Pending
      approvalStatus là summary state trên guestbook entry.
      Nếu có report lifecycle riêng, source of truth vẫn ở moderationReports.
    end note
